'''Chief Petty Officer'''<ref name="HC 48">{{HelmetCollectionCite|48|Weapons & Uniforms}}</ref> was a [[Navy|naval]] [[Military rank|rank]].<ref name="TFAVD" /> Around [[34 ABY]],<ref name="GA">''[[Star Wars: Galactic Atlas]]''</ref> [[Nastia Unamo]] held that rank aboard the [[First Order]] [[starship]] ''[[Finalizer]]''.<ref name="TFAVD" /> [[Standard decade|Decades]] earlier, [[Corla Metonae]] was chief petty officer aboard the [[House of Organa|RHA]] ''[[Tantive IV]]''.<ref name="Raymus" />

